videos.headline: Miss State strikes first behind Gibson's TD scamper
videos.description: Nick Gibson slices through the Ole Miss defense to give the Bulldogs the game's first points with a 27-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miss State strikes first behind Gibson's TD scamper) 2019/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Plumlee punches in Ole Miss TD
videos.description: John Rhys Plumlee cuts Ole Miss' deficit in half with a two-yard touchdown midway through the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Plumlee punches in Ole Miss TD) 2019/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Ealy lunges into end zone for TD
videos.description: Ole Miss RB Jerrion Ealy knots the score at 14-14 before halftime with a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss' Ealy lunges into end zone for TD) 2019/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shrader shreds Ole Miss defense for TD
videos.description: Garrett Shrader keeps it himself on a run-pass-option and dices into the end zone for a 5-yard Mississippi State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shrader shreds Ole Miss defense for TD) 2019/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luke describes Moore's celebration penalty as 'disappointing'
videos.description: Matt Luke reacts to Ole Miss' loss to Mississippi State and Elijah Moore's unsportsmanlike penalty in the game's waning moments.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Luke describes Moore's celebration penalty as 'disappointing') 2019/11/29

videos.headline: Flashback: Ole Miss flushes away a chance at the Golden Egg
videos.description: Mississippi State escapes with a 21-20 victory after Ole Miss WR Elijah Moore was penalized for celebrating a touchdown by pretending to urinate like a dog and the Rebels missed the ensuing extra point.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Flashback: Ole Miss flushes away a chance at the Golden Egg) 2020/03/23 ESHEET SC
